text: Marcin Waliński (born 24 October 1990) is a Polish volleyball player, a member of Ślepsk Suwałki, PlusLiga. ==Career== He was appointed to the Polish national team by Stéphane Antiga in 2015. In June 2018, he signed a two–year contract with the Polish club Aluron Virtu Warta Zawiercie. ==External links== * Player profile at CEV.eu * Player profile at PlusLiga.pl * Player profile at Volleybox.net ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:People from Trzcianka Category:Sportspeople from Greater Poland Voivodeship Category:Polish men's volleyball players Category:Łuczniczka Bydgoszcz players Category:AZS Olsztyn players Category:Warta Zawiercie players Category:Ślepsk Suwałki players
